data.text: @RebeccaRacer @gmracingblue Watched all the shows with Elo back to back really enjoyed them 👍 any more coming up ?

@RebeccaRacer It so sad that are society has reached to this point that Closing a Car door is such a BiG deal.... 😳😳There is so more important things to talk, resolve, and make right in this world... #ComeOnPeople..

@RebeccaRacer Haha... done this in the rally car when we're both strapped in and theres no one close to get the attention of. Hard acceleration usually works! Tricky for you on a grid doing that though! 😆

@RebeccaRacer Also, it depends on the car, for example you may need someone to help shut the door in a Delorean as it is quite difficult to reach the straps apparently once you are inside!! 😀😀 https://t.co/JJn6jgnyX7
@RebeccaRacer It’s just good old fashioned manners to open and close a door for a lady, at least that’s what I think 🤔❤️
